Author: fishonthesun
Text: All of this is really awesome! I hope you continue to work on feeling out what's good for you. If it makes you feel better, to an outsider it sounds like the exercise you're doing is very healthy, most likely not too much. I hope you can keep working on reducing the b/p- it's awesome how much you have so far!! I'm really proud of you (even tho I don't know you lol)
